    .row
      .default-text
        h2 Form best practices

        p The combination of complex forms and less technical customers gives input design a higher-than-average importance. We adapted best practices from Neilsen , with a framework that supported a wide variety of labels, placeholders, informational text, and alarts.

    //- desktop version
