    .row
      .default-text
        h2 Empty states and file uploads

        p Onboarding is a difficult but critical step for financial applications. A multitiude of empty states helped users familiarize themselves with the UI before the system was populated with their information. Some states are purely informational, and some have calls to action at various levels of intensity.

    .panel.panel--remitly-pale
      .row
        .col-sm-20.col-sm-offset-2.col-md-18.col-md-offset-3.shadow.card
            img(src="/img/remitly/remitly_empty_states.png", style="width: 100%;")

    .row
      .default-text
        h2 Tiered error states

        p When things go wrong, it’s important to be clear about where. Multiple patterns give the option to couple an error tightly with a piece of UI, or message it more generally.

    .panel.panel--remitly-pale
      .hidden-xs.hidden-sm.row(style="display:flex; flex-direction: row; padding: 0 60px")
        .col-xs-6.col-xs-offset-0(style="display: flex; flex: 1 100%; flex-direction: column")
          img.shadow(src="/img/remitly/remitly_error_field.png", style="width: 100%;")
          div(style="padding-top: 20px")  
            h3 Field level
            p When a problem is scoped to a single UI element.

        .col-xs-6.col-xs-offset-1(style="display: flex; flex: 1 100%; flex-direction: column")
          img.shadow(src="/img/remitly/remitly_error_form.png", style="width: 100%;")
          div(style="padding-top: 20px")  
            h3 Form level
            p Errors on a single part of the page, but not tied to a single UI element.

        .col-xs-6.col-xs-offset-1(style="display: flex; flex: 1 100%; flex-direction: column")
          img.shadow(src="/img/remitly/remitly_error_system.png", style="width: 100%;")
          div(style="padding-top: 20px")  
            h3 System level
            p Errors above the page level, like a vendor outage or local connectivity issue.

      .hidden-md.hidden-lg.row
        .shadow.col-xs-18.col-xs-offset-3(style="background: white; margin-bottom: 40px;")
          img(src="/img/remitly/remitly_error_field.png", style="width: 100%;")
          div(style="padding: 0 20px 20px;")
            h3 Field level
            p When a problem is scoped to a single UI element.

        .shadow.col-xs-18.col-xs-offset-3(style="background: white; margin-bottom: 40px;")
          img(src="/img/remitly/remitly_error_form.png", style="width: 100%;")
